========================================
Group Policy Configuration Summary
========================================

[Overview]
Group Policy settings were configured to enforce secure authentication
and reduce the risk of unauthorized access.

[Password Policy]
- Minimum Password Length  : 8 characters
- Password Complexity      : Enabled
- Password History         : Enabled

[Account Lockout Policy]
- Lockout Threshold        : 5 failed attempts
- Lockout Duration         : 15 minutes
- Reset Counter After      : 15 minutes

[Purpose]
These configurations help protect against brute-force, dictionary,
and hybrid password attacks while enforcing strong authentication practices.
